'Malakeng is a community council located in the Mafeteng District of Lesotho. Its population in 2006 was 8,382.\n\n
(6003) 1988 VO is a main-belt minor planet. It was discovered by Seiji Ueda and Hiroshi Kaneda in Kushiro, Hokkaidō, Japan, on November 2, 1988.\n\n
(6476) 1987 VT is a main-belt minor planet. It was discovered by Zdeňka Vávrová at the Kleť Observatory near České Budějovice, Czech Republic, on November 15, 1987.\n\n
